        public static LinkedHashMap<String,​String> translate_map​(String from,
                                                               String to,
                                                               String text)
                                                        throws IOException
        Returns an hashmap with source's translated chunks. This is a quick implementation, multiple chunks with the same translation will be outputed just once. Also, Google translation removes some punctuation.
        Parameters:
        from - The source language code
        to - The translated language code
        text - The text to translate
